{"tid":1917324,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得做人真係好辛苦","createTime":"2020-03-09T12:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T12:40:31.000Z","uid":45923,"like":63,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"fa84155ffe2e6154b0d85b076f29eccb562ebcff","tid":1917324,"uid":45923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:22:10.000Z","msg":"人愈大就發覺自己愈來愈唔識同人相處<br />\n以前覺得出到來做野聽教聽話，就一定唔會得罪人。原來一樣都會討人厭。<br />\n成日都俾人話唔識諗多步、唔識話頭醒尾。<br />\n我認我資質好差、好蠢、好鈍。我真係唔知點樣去學好喱個課題。<br />\n感覺好似我無論點做都係錯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512d72ba15718b3f9218575494608a4067698edb","tid":1917324,"uid":337986,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"窮人做人先辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24a2dd1e8b13e4c0f6efa3005c61678fc49eb64","tid":1917324,"uid":123848,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:32:45.000Z","msg":"聽教聽話就會諗多步啦"},{"pid":"5537b47553c54faa1894792aeaaf2d9bb82b5ac6","tid":1917324,"uid":45923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"512d72ba15718b3f9218575494608a4067698edb","tid":1917324,"uid":337986,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"窮人做人先辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:56:05.000Z","msg":"窮人就幾時都係辛苦命架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf25979e92ee67cc3c7f46ef0142f54ad3363a9e","tid":1917324,"uid":45923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c24a2dd1e8b13e4c0f6efa3005c61678fc49eb64","tid":1917324,"uid":123848,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:32:45.000Z","msg":"聽教聽話就會諗多步啦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:59:41.000Z","msg":"聽教聽話，人地叫我做乜我都會照做，唔會多唔會少。<br />\n人地叫我跪我唔敢坐，咁就會俾人話你踢一踢先郁一郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6960df7e4879ff37e93457066c1cb308ab05